{"tid":995042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"苦版王祖賢來台賣淫 15歲開始做雞每次實拿20元 28歲已4度墮胎","createTime":"2019-01-25T07:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T07:48:48.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc32175f2e60c8fbb3a6606a8e5fc9c0ebfe1b2","tid":995042,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:00:55.000Z","msg":"南部警方在農曆春節前展開查緝情色集團專案，近日派員明察暗訪，得知一名容貌神似影星王祖賢的中國女子「小如」被安排到台灣賣淫，打出高CP值吸客。另外也有東南亞外籍賣淫女子來台後，就被關在陰暗房間接客，直到完成履約，離台時才能重見天日。警方表示，已經掌握相關情資，將報請檢察官指揮，查緝不法。<br />\n<br />\n台南市警方探訪舊城區的情色集團情資，得知「暗黑版王祖賢」的中國女子小如賣淫坎坷人生，根據坊間情資指出，小如曾向台灣友人表示，未成年時曾遭性侵，15歲被騙去當雛妓，性交易1次實拿20元人民幣，至今28歲已4度墮胎，日前第1次來台賣淫就遇到奧客。<br />\n <br />\n小如自知賣淫容易染病，為了安全，她接客時都會要求對方戴保險套，但來台後接觸的首名客人竟趁機「拔套」辦事，小如氣得要業者幫忙討公道，經客人討價還價，最後以多付2000元「賠償」小如。<br />\n <br />\n另外，警方也得知，南部地區某情色集團從東南亞引進外籍女子，一下機就接走團員，隨即安排套房讓外籍女子定點賣淫。女子從一下飛機就被關在陰暗房間，1張床用來接客也用來睡覺，直到接客人數達到契約簽訂的數量，才算「結束營業」，準備離台時才能走出室外。<br />\n <br />\n警方表示，近年來與移民署、海巡署積極查緝外籍或大陸人士來台非法打工或從事不法行為，只要掌握相關事證，辦案人員就報請檢察官指揮偵辦，務必阻絕外籍人士在台灣從事不法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190125/640_a27c21f809aa95f10a0a46c1ad342a74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190125%2F640_a27c21f809aa95f10a0a46c1ad342a74.jpg&h=91975a83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20190125/1507080/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20190125%2F1507080%2F&d=1JqvwWNHjQPDp8tWt%2FwICo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=fd1070dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20190125%2F1507080%2F&h=58f0fd0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20190125/1507080/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同事剛娶了隻30歲大陸妹 , 恭喜晒"},{"pid":"dc0bf431ee21622a937aef9f5473b40faf0af9a6","tid":995042,"uid":89665,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:03:49.000Z","msg":"邊到似王祖賢"},{"pid":"02ba69c84512e9a77a8f1cc6ead53217d6664a89","tid":995042,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6fc8d59983fc91418193b1819f3643af4e64005","tid":995042,"uid":69168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:04:54.000Z","msg":"似王祖藍多啲"},{"pid":"48820c5a05939bde7597b9c7983ea1cbdbd3db1b","tid":995042,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02ba69c84512e9a77a8f1cc6ead53217d6664a89","tid":995042,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:05:21.000Z","msg":"但來台後接觸的首名客人竟趁機「拔套」辦事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n共實PTGF可以用依招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca782aae4970e2e5bbcf1db0edb6cdea6cdae4c","tid":995042,"uid":3189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20130624/large/1372087626_ff0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20130624%2Flarge%2F1372087626_ff0a.jpg&h=f50c3c4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c157e0a41577582c356fe3e9f29bf461fbe457f9","tid":995042,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:18:56.000Z","msg":"恭喜樓主個同事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53d9793eecc9ce063b941cc65f08d8ddf5f0393","tid":995042,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6fc8d59983fc91418193b1819f3643af4e64005","tid":995042,"uid":69168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T07:04:54.000Z","msg